data.description: Welcome to your new East Memphis home! This charming 4 Bed, 2.5 bath home offers the perfect blend of classic elegance and modern comfort. Situated on a wooded corner lot, this home offers over 2200 sf for you to call home.  Complete with spacious bedrooms, a 2 car garage, privacy-fenced backyard featuring a cozy patio area boasting beautiful landscaping, and much, much more, this is a home you don't want to miss.
